    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I needed a quick and dirty reference for the Markdown syntax.  Voila.  The raw Markdown Cheat Sheet file (in GitHub flavored Markdown) is <a href="https://github.com/chrissimpkins/markdown-cheat-sheet/blob/master/MD-cheat-sheet.md">available on GitHub</a> with a <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/deed.en_US">Creative Commons license</a>.</p>

<!--More-->


