<h1>Typography</h1>

<h3 id="heading">Headings <a href="#top"><i class="icon-circle-arrow-up"></i></a></h3>


<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Heading Markdown</span><a href='http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax#header'>Gruber Docs</a></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt; = # Header
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h2&gt; = ## Header
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h3&gt; = ### Header
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h4&gt; = #### Header
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h5&gt; = ##### Header
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h6&gt; = ###### Header</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<h3 id="paragraph">Paragraphs <a href="#top"><i class="icon-circle-arrow-up"></i></a></h3>


<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Paragraph Markdown</span><a href='http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax#p'>Gruber Docs</a></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>This is the first paragraph.
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>And this is the second separated by a blank line.
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<h3 id="bold">Bold Text <a href="#top"><i class="icon-circle-arrow-up"></i></a></h3>


<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Bold Text Markdown</span><a href='http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax#em'>Gruber Docs</a></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>In this sentence the word **bold** is tagged with &lt;strong&gt; tags.</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<h3 id="italic">Italicized Text <a href="#top"><i class="icon-circle-arrow-up"></i></a></h3>


<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Italicized Text</span><a href='http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax#em'>Gruber Docs</a></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>In this sentence the word *italics* is tagged with &lt;em&gt; tags.</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<h3 id="blockquote">Blockquotes <a href="#top"><i class="icon-circle-arrow-up"></i></a></h3>


<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Blockquotes Markdown</span><a href='http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax#blockquote'>Gruber Docs</a></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
<span class='line-number'>14</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>/***********************************
</span><span class='line'>* Standard Blockquote
</span><span class='line'>***********************************/
</span><span class='line'>&gt; This is a block
</span><span class='line'>&gt; of really cool
</span><span class='line'>&gt; text
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>/***********************************
</span><span class='line'>* Nested Blockquote
</span><span class='line'>***********************************/
</span><span class='line'>&gt; Here is a block
</span><span class='line'>&gt; that contains
</span><span class='line'>&gt;&gt; a nest!
</span><span class='line'>&gt; and I'm back out of the nest...</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<h3 id="list">Lists <a href="#top"><i class="icon-circle-arrow-up"></i></a></h3>


<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Lists Markdown</span><a href='http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax#list'>Gruber Docs</a></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
