</span><span class='line'>- list item 3
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>/***********************************
</span><span class='line'>* Ordered List
</span><span class='line'>***********************************/
</span><span class='line'>1. list item 1
</span><span class='line'>2. list item 2
</span><span class='line'>  1. sublist 1
</span><span class='line'>  2. sublist 2
</span><span class='line'>3. list item 3
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h1>Links</h1>

<h3 id="inlinelink">Inline Link <a href="#top"><i class="icon-circle-arrow-up"></i></a></h3>


<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Inline Link Markdown</span><a href='http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax#link'>Gruber Docs</a></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>This is a line with an [inline link to Google](http://www.google.com "Google").</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<h3 id="reflink">Reference Links <a href="#top"><i class="icon-circle-arrow-up"></i></a></h3>


<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Reference Links Markdown</span><a href='http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax#link'>Gruber Docs</a></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>This line has reference links for [Google] [1] and [GitHub] [2].
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>  [1]: http://www.google.com "Google"
</span><span class='line'>  [2]: http://www.github.com "GitHub"</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h1>Tables</h1>

<h3 id="table">Standard Table <a href="#top"><i class="icon-circle-arrow-up"></i></a></h3>


<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Standard Table Markdown</span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
