<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Code Block Markdown</span><a href='https://help.github.com/articles/github-flavored-markdown#fenced-code-blocks'>GitHub Docs</a></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
