<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
<span class='line-number'>14</span>
<span class='line-number'>15</span>
<span class='line-number'>16</span>
<span class='line-number'>17</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>/***********************************
</span><span class='line'>* Standard Code Block
</span><span class='line'>***********************************/
</span><span class='line'>Tab or four spaces for standard code block syntax:
</span><span class='line'>  void replace(){
</span><span class='line'>      //lots of really cool code in here
</span><span class='line'>  }
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>/******************************************************
</span><span class='line'>* GitHub Flavored Code Block with Syntax Highlighting
</span><span class='line'>*******************************************************/
</span><span class='line'>Three ticks before and after the code block & specify language:
</span><span class='line'>  ```language
